      "description": "Offered is a museum-quality 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This specimen boasts a flawless Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Technical highlights include a documented subframe reinforcement, comprehensive VANOS overhaul, and rod bearing replacement, ensuring mechanical longevity and peak performance. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, paired with untouched OEM suspension for an authentic M-division driving signature. Finished in Titanium Silver over Black Nappa leather, the car exhibits zero oxidation, no bolster wear, and no interior delamination. This is a turn-key, investment-grade example for the meticulous purist.",
